PS2LS
=====

A toolkit for inspecting Planetside 2 and Forgelight files

Contribute on IRC: #REside on irc.planetside-universe.com


Building
=====
Project was created with Visual Studio 2012.  

You need OpenTK: http://www.opentk.com/


Credits
=====
